{"tid":1993953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不怕中國經濟報復　澳洲總理堅持獨立調查武肺起源","createTime":"2020-04-29T06:43:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T07:16:12.000Z","uid":227801,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a2223138582b4d6b627c8bf16fe50cbdf73e704","tid":1993953,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:43:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200429/3H4JTLPLBUFRQR5HYVY5AUQ4ZY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200429%2F3H4JTLPLBUFRQR5HYVY5AUQ4ZY%2F&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImOL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=8b423237\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200429%2F3H4JTLPLBUFRQR5HYVY5AUQ4ZY%2F&h=928e9b19\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200429/3H4JTLPLBUFRQR5HYVY5AUQ4ZY/</a><br />\n澳洲政府最近提出武漢肺炎（COVID-19）疫情源頭展開獨立調查，引發中國不滿，並揚言進行經濟報復。澳洲總理莫里森（Scott Morrison）今日（4/29）強調，澳洲要求獨立調查疫情絕對合理，更不是針對中國而來。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森在記者會上說：「澳洲所推動的調查並無針對性。這個病毒奪走全球逾20萬條人命，重創經濟。這場疫情所代表的意義和影響程度無以倫比。全世界現在要求進行獨立調查，看起來實在非常合理和明智。」<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n路透報導，自從莫里森發起要對新冠病毒起源展開獨立調查後，澳洲與中國之間的關係惡化。報導分析，雖然莫里森強調此舉並非針對中國，但看在澳洲最大貿易夥伴中國的眼裡卻不是這麼回事，而澳洲勢必將繼續受到北京施壓。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n中國駐澳大使成競業日前接受《澳洲金融評論》訪問時表示，澳洲要調查病毒起源，此舉「危險」，且會導致中國反彈，他說，中國可以拒買澳洲紅酒與牛肉，中國人民也可以不到澳洲旅行、留學。（桂家齊／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"aa5639d10d3991d5e170fe54a11d5d2b0d2e5ff3","tid":1993953,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"唔再鬧Scomo同Dutton了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf0c83ec4f5b1a45c16852aee437b4771b85ebf","tid":1993953,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"終於爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反天黑國同歐豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bec60fda2107ad04b86c5670a8fc0a5f42f276","tid":1993953,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf0c83ec4f5b1a45c16852aee437b4771b85ebf","tid":1993953,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:52:12.000Z","msg":"終於爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反天黑國同歐豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"其實睇番歷史，<br />\n歐洲取態真係唔重要，佢地其實當上個世紀冇分別。<br />\n二戰唔係美國，歐洲已經得番一個國家。"}]}